549
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:14,500
You read my diary?

550
00:37:14,500 --> 00:37:18,011
If I didn't, how would I know what you are busy with all day long?

551
00:37:22,700 --> 00:37:25,430
"I can't believe I lost to him in the game room."

552
00:37:25,430 --> 00:37:27,320
Mom, stop reading it!

553
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:29,080
This is what you wrote.

554
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:31,090
Why can't you hear it?

555
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,920
Give it to me.

556
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:36,300
Give me the diary.

557
00:37:37,390 --> 00:37:39,300
If you don't give it to me, this will not end easily for you.

558
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:41,949
Give it to me. What are you doing? Give it.

559
00:37:45,460 --> 00:37:47,210
Are you happy now?

560
00:37:47,940 --> 00:37:50,020
I will never write diaries again.

561
00:37:50,825 --> 00:37:53,300
Suit yourself.

562
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:54,950
I'm telling you, Ding Xian.

563
00:37:54,950 --> 00:37:57,087
You are grounded forever.

564
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:23,950
What are you doing?

565
00:38:23,950 --> 00:38:26,040
I had a spat with my mom.

566
00:38:26,040 --> 00:38:28,060
And I threw my diary out.

567
00:38:30,570 --> 00:38:32,580
Are you sure you dropped it here?

568
00:38:42,700 --> 00:38:43,910
Hey.

569
00:38:44,570 --> 00:38:47,320
I just saw a scavenger pass by and head in that direction.

570
00:38:53,430 --> 00:38:56,390
Hello, have you seen a scavenger nearby?

571
00:38:56,390 --> 00:38:58,270
He's long gone.

572
00:38:59,133 --> 00:39:00,833
He's gone?

573
00:39:13,530 --> 00:39:15,230
Stop crying.

574
00:39:22,150 --> 00:39:24,050
I'm fine.

575
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:31,300
It's okay if I can't find it.

576
00:39:43,050 --> 00:39:45,430
If you don't want to go home,

577
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:49,250
come hang out at my place.

578
