592
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:10,590
I'm fine with either one.

593
00:41:10,590 --> 00:41:11,990
All right.

594
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:14,570
I'll go boil the water.

595
00:41:20,287 --> 00:41:22,309
The noodles are ready.

596
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:38,000
This is the first time I've had instant noodles.

597
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:40,500
My mom won't let me have any.

598
